#: ../../changelog.rst:168
msgid ""
"Initial support for client side field level encryption. See the docstring"
" for :class:`~pymongo.mongo_client.MongoClient`, "
":class:`~pymongo.encryption_options.AutoEncryptionOpts`, and "
":mod:`~pymongo.encryption` for details. **Note: Support for client side "
