msgid ""
":meth:`~pymongo.database.Database.current_op` now always uses the "
"``Database``'s  :attr:`~pymongo.database.Database.codec_options` when "
"decoding the command response. Previously the codec_options was only used"
" when the MongoDB server version was <= 3.0."
msgstr ""

#: ../../changelog.rst:287
msgid ""
"Undeprecated "
":meth:`~pymongo.mongo_client.MongoClient.get_default_database` and added "
"the ``default`` parameter."
